1
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:15,200
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:41,130
[My Dear Guardian]

3
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:44,209
[Episode 14]

4
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,400
Zhuo Ran.

5
00:01:51,010 --> 00:01:51,690
Did you notice that

6
00:01:51,770 --> 00:01:53,959
you're especially unlucky
when you're with me?

7
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,340
You either injure yourself or fall sick.

8
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:59,320
Perhaps we're not meant to be together.

9
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:00,880
How about this?

10
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:04,400
I'll stay away from you.

11
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:12,880
I know I'm quite annoying at times.

12
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:18,630
Mi Gu.

13
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,560
It's not your fault.

14
00:02:21,930 --> 00:02:23,400
I don't mind.

15
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,440
Did I interrupt you?

16
00:02:32,170 --> 00:02:33,800
We're coming in.

17
00:02:34,810 --> 00:02:37,070
Hello, Mr Zhuo and Ms Mi.

18
00:02:37,250 --> 00:02:39,300
With regard to the incident

19
00:02:39,529 --> 00:02:40,930
outside the banquet hall at the hotel,

20
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:43,240
it's indeed tricky and troublesome.

21
00:02:43,610 --> 00:02:45,770
Now, we need cooperation
from both of you

22
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:47,000
to give a statement.

23
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:49,170
He's still bleeding.

24
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:50,130
Can we do it later?

25
00:02:50,210 --> 00:02:51,120
No.

26
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:53,000
Please cooperate with us.
It won't be long.

27
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:54,800
-You...
-Mi Gu.

28
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:56,730
It's okay.

29
00:02:56,810 --> 00:02:57,770
Do we do it together or...

30
00:02:57,860 --> 00:02:58,880
Do it separately.

31
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:00,200
Come with me.

32
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:07,980
He's a lunatic.

33
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,690
He's been pestering me a long time
insisting to date me.

34
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:10,850
Have you ever given him any promises?

35
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:11,990
Of course not.

36
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,400
I don't know.

37
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:16,360
Don't know?

38
00:03:17,390 --> 00:03:19,220
Ms Mi Gu and I

39
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:20,920
met each other not long ago.

40
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,529
I'm not quite familiar

41
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,080
with her romantic experience.

42
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,200
So,

43
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:27,830
both of you are not close with each other?

44
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:30,360
Yes, you may say so.

45
00:03:30,930 --> 00:03:32,440
All thanks to Zhuo Ran.

46
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:34,330
That's why I escaped.

47
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:35,170
Why did he

48
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:37,000
ask for your help to obtain
the licence of the forum?

49
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:38,410
He's a businessman.

50
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,110
Isn't it normal for him
to expand his connection?

51
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,620
I couldn't help but wonder

52
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:45,100
why you chose to attend

53
00:03:45,279 --> 00:03:47,060
a medicine related forum?

54
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,510
My company

55
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,710
is mainly about 3D printing.

56
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:53,110
Lately, we're doing a collaboration

57
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,700
with the hospital.

58
00:03:54,790 --> 00:03:56,430
Therefore, I'm interested
to get an understanding

59
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,330
of the related industry information.

60
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,470
You're indeed far-sighted

61
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,820
and in the full vigour of life.

62
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,570
Do you know this person?

63
00:04:10,130 --> 00:04:11,010
No.

64
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,310
No.

65
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,610
Does Zhuo Ran know him?

66
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,100
How do I know?

67
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,660
Why do you keep asking about Zhuo Ran?

68
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,300
He's not the person who assaulted me.

69
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:25,020
We need to get a better understanding
of every detail at the scene.

70
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,190
Take off your shirt.

71
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:28,950
We received complaints
from the public

72
00:04:29,030 --> 00:04:30,540
that you

73
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:32,270
illegally possessed a gun.

74
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,780
We need to confirm on that.

75
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,850
Can you give me a hand?

76
00:04:37,930 --> 00:04:39,270
Okay, no problem.

77
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:49,710
What a nice material.

78
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:57,340
Please raise your hands.

79
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,890
It seems that it was just a mischief.

80
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:11,710
Mr Zhuo, I'm so sorry.

81
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,420
People who simply take up police resources

82
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,780
should be taught a lesson.

83
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:17,940
That's all for today.

84
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,940
You're working for the people.

85
00:05:21,030 --> 00:05:21,670
I can understand that.

86
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,010
All right, see you again.

87
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:31,010
Please sign the document
if everything is okay.

88
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,740
It's not working.

89
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,820
Do you have any other pen?

90
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,200
I have a pen.

91
00:05:51,970 --> 00:05:52,850
Do you?

92
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,020
It's done.

93
00:06:00,890 --> 00:06:01,770
Use it.

94
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,740
Thank you for your cooperation.

95
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,470
What do you keep in your bag?

96
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,610
It looks quite heavy.

97
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:30,650
It's camera.
I need it for working purposes.

98
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,040
Let's go.

99
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,660
Mi Gu.

100
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,500
It's not your fault.

101
00:07:00,380 --> 00:07:02,470
I heard from my dad
that someone assaulted you.

102
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,660
Are you okay?

103
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,020
Are you injured?

104
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:08,420
I'm fine.

105
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,630
Zhuo Ran injured himself though.

106
00:07:12,110 --> 00:07:13,090
Is it serious?

107
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:14,950
According to the doctor,

108
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,780
his nerves and bones are intact.

109
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,930
I think he should be fine.

110
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,180
Where is he?

111
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,500
He's undergoing debridement.

112
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,250
Well...

113
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:35,180
I went to the hotel
for film shooting on location.

114
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:38,260
He was there to attend a medical forum.

115
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,490
We...

116
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,350
We were there for work

117
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,570
and we ran into each other by chance.

118
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,660
Something unexpected occurred.

119
00:07:46,230 --> 00:07:47,390
As he's bleeding profusely,

120
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,290
-I sent him to the hospital.
-Actually...

121
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,859
Don't mind it.

122
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,980
Take a seat.

123
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,180
I mean,

124
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,420
to Zhuo Ran, I...

125
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:12,780
Yes.

126
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,140
When I saw him,

127
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,150
I still felt something

128
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,810
which couldn't be explained.

129
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:18,940
However, I think

130
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,770
it's not because of him per se

131
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:25,050
but it's because of the memories.

132
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:28,360
Everything in the past happened for real

133
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:30,240
and it won't happen again in the future.

134
00:08:30,970 --> 00:08:32,860
Hence, I won't forget it.

135
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,940
Sometimes, we couldn't help reminiscing

136
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:40,660
those guys in white shirts

137
00:08:40,999 --> 00:08:42,940
who played basketball on the court.

138
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,830
However, it's just nostalgia.

139
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,379
Life goes on no matter what.

140
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,780
The story between Zhuo Ran
and I has ended.

141
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,860
As for you,

142
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:01,050
if he really makes you happy,

143
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:03,120
then you should go ahead.

144
00:09:09,310 --> 00:09:10,580
I thought

145
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,180
you wouldn't talk to me anymore.

146
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,260
Just because of a former lover?

147
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,890
Am I so petty?

148
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,340
To me,

149
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,780
a serious friendship

150
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,780
is more memorable than
romantic relationship.

151
00:09:29,990 --> 00:09:31,300
I love you, Mi Gu.

152
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,970
Any man

153
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,630
can never take your place in my heart.

154
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,380
I've to get back to work.

155
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:00,740
Call me if anything.

156
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:32,150
Why did you bring me to the hospital?

157
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,190
Didn't I tell you to send me home?

158
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:34,420
We're here to apologise.

159
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:35,490
What?

160
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:37,030
Hello.

161
00:10:37,110 --> 00:10:37,470
Hello.

162
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,580
Is Xia Chu here?

163
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:39,710
I think she went to the emergency ward.

164
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,910
You may give her a call.

165
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,170
All right, thank you.

166
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:44,620
-I don't want to go there.
-Let's go.

167
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:57,420
Thank you for your help at the hotel.

168
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:59,260
Have you taken the medicine?

169
00:11:00,370 --> 00:11:01,310
What?

170
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,370
-What are you doing?
-It's tranquillizer.

171
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:10,540
I told Mi Gu to replace the tranquillizer.

172
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,980
Have you taken it?

173
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:14,370
The tranquillizer is not for myself.

174
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,220
I gave it to Liang Mu Ze.

175
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,780
Tell him to throw it away.

176
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:19,860
What's wrong?

177
00:11:21,330 --> 00:11:23,710
My company had a collaboration
with a medicine manufacturer before.

178
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:25,670
We attempted to use 3D printing technology

179
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:27,610
to produce hypnotic
which is made of Chinese medicine.

180
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:29,610
However, the first batch

181
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:31,420
contains excessive birthwort.

182
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:33,510
Long term consumption

183
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:36,500
may lead to kidney failure
or worse, liver cancer.

184
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:38,760
Hence, we decided to destroy the products.

185
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:41,270
My assistant took it by mistake.

186
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:42,860
I didn't know that

187
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:44,320
and I gave it to Mi Gu.

188
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,550
Normally, when a man and a woman
are together

189
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:51,230
and they did not pick up the phone call
at first instance,

190
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,670
it's either they're busy
or they're having fun.

191
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,980
Don't ask for embarrassment.

192
00:11:58,370 --> 00:11:59,610
Xia Chu.

193
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:02,110
It was an accident.

194
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,720
Luckily nothing happened to you.

195
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,420
I'm fine

196
00:12:11,610 --> 00:12:13,000
but my friend almost took

197
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,260
substandard medicine.

198
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:15,170
Do you know

199
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:16,530
how much of trouble you caused me?

200
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:17,940
If his health is affected

201
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:19,450
because of my negligence,

202
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:21,640
I won't be able to forgive myself.

203
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:23,330
Also,

204
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:24,540
before you make any decision

205
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:26,160
that has something to do with me,

206
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,250
will you please

207
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:28,620
inform me about it?

208
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:29,890
Don't simply do whatever you want.

209
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:32,260
Don't get Mi Gu
involved in your so-called accidents.

210
00:12:32,350 --> 00:12:33,900
Please don't hurt me over and over again

211
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,640
in the name of protecting me.

212
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:37,600
I'm sorry.

213
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:49,530
She looks like she's having fun.

214
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:58,400
Where did you go?

215
00:12:58,910 --> 00:12:59,800
Take a guess.

216
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,240
Where did you find her?

217
00:13:17,780 --> 00:13:18,880
Well...

218
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:22,160
Sorry to have troubled you
to pick her up at the airport.

219
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:25,240
Mu Ze.

220
00:13:26,270 --> 00:13:27,320
I'm tired.

221
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:32,420
She...

222
00:13:32,700 --> 00:13:33,380
What's wrong?

223
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:34,460
She fell asleep due to her illness.

224
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:35,800
Let's go to your office.

225
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:37,760
Let's go.

226
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,320
Zhuo Ran.

227
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:49,640
You're still here.

228
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:52,000
I went to pick up the medicine.

229
00:13:52,780 --> 00:13:53,530
The doctor prescribed medicine

230
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:55,010
for tetanus and antibiotics.

231
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,990
Thank you.

232
00:13:57,620 --> 00:13:58,970
Let's go to the injection room.

233
00:14:00,310 --> 00:14:01,320
Okay.

234
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:15,940
Do you plan to leave her here?

235
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,850
Yes, if I send her home,

236
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:18,920
she'll run away once she's awake.

237
00:14:21,380 --> 00:14:22,800
Even if you leave her here,

238
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:25,000
I can't be watching her all the time.

239
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:26,400
Are you busy?

240
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:27,640
Of course.

241
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:29,380
At night, if any emergency

242
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,580
happens to any of the patients,

243
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:32,330
I have to handle it at the first instance.

244
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:34,810
Why were you

245
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:36,410
hugging a man in the lift?

246
00:14:42,900 --> 00:14:44,620
The test result of the medicine is out.

247
00:14:44,700 --> 00:14:45,600
I know.

248
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:48,410
It's Chinese medicine
produced by 3D printing technology.

249
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:50,770
Zhang Yi Chi told you that?

250
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:52,450
No, it's Zhuo Ran.

251
00:14:53,140 --> 00:14:54,400
Zhuo Ran told you about it?

252
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:57,530
He told his assistant to get the medicine.

253
00:14:57,950 --> 00:14:59,200
His assistant got confused.

254
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:03,370
-So, he's the one who gave it to Mi Gu?
-Yes.

255
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:06,210
However, he didn't know that
his assistant made a mistake.

256
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:08,440
Was that his explanation?

257
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:10,100
I believe that it's the truth.

258
00:15:10,190 --> 00:15:11,180
Otherwise, he wouldn't
have had come to to see me

259
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:12,440
at the first instance.

260
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,040
Did he know that
I was testing the medicine?

261
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:17,480
I didn't tell him anything.

262
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:18,680
How about Mi Gu?

263
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:23,960
I'm not sure of that.

264
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,280
He's...

265
00:15:27,180 --> 00:15:28,530
trying to get us before we get him.

266
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:31,130
It's just an accident.

267
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:33,000
You don't have to come down
on him too hard.

268
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:35,900
Accident?

269
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,170
Of course it's an accident.

270
00:15:37,260 --> 00:15:37,970
Otherwise,

271
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,250
why would Zhuo Ran harm me?

272
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,170
The medicine was for me.

273
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:42,560
He didn't know that.

274
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:44,170
How did he know
that you have the medicine?

275
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:49,890
How did he know?

276
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:11,180
For a very long time

277
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,810
after he left,

278
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:14,780
I could only fall asleep

279
00:16:14,870 --> 00:16:16,090
with the help of drugs.

280
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:18,680
When I had insomnia,

281
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:21,080
I sent many emails to him.

282
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:22,610
In some emails, I scolded him.

283
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,400
In some, I begged of him.

284
00:16:25,060 --> 00:16:26,600
He didn't reply any of the emails.

285
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:29,170
