Zhuo Ran.

569
00:30:05,650 --> 00:30:06,560
I'm home.

570
00:30:10,810 --> 00:30:11,820
You should go up.

571
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:14,300
Hold on.

572
00:30:28,690 --> 00:30:29,830
I've something to return to you.

573
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:31,770
Is this yours?

574
00:30:37,130 --> 00:30:39,070
Don't you think you need to explain to me?

575
00:30:42,300 --> 00:30:43,580
I'm exhausted, Mi Gu.

576
00:30:43,670 --> 00:30:44,820
I'm exhausted too.

577
00:30:44,990 --> 00:30:46,810
I was on tenterhooks at the hospital.

578
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:47,540
I wanted to ask you

579
00:30:47,630 --> 00:30:49,120
but I worried that someone
might find out about it.

580
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:50,960
Where did it come from?

581
00:30:51,050 --> 00:30:52,910
Why did you keep a gun with you?

582
00:31:05,890 --> 00:31:06,910
It's fake.

583
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,570
It's just a toy.

584
00:31:20,190 --> 00:31:22,080
Then why didn't you inform me before hand?

585
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,840
It was an emergency.

586
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:25,450
I did it subconsciously.

587
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:29,330
You knew that the police officers
would conduct a search on you.

588
00:31:29,580 --> 00:31:32,040
I only know that all the police officers
in the world are the same.

589
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:34,100
If they found out that

590
00:31:34,190 --> 00:31:35,640
I brought a toy gun with me,

591
00:31:36,030 --> 00:31:38,010
they would interrogate me non-stop

592
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:40,760
and then choose to believe
what they want to believe.

593
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:42,420
I didn't want to put myself in trouble.

594
00:31:42,510 --> 00:31:44,120
What if I got myself into trouble?

595
00:31:45,670 --> 00:31:47,610
If that ever happened,

596
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:49,570
I would explain to them.

597
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:56,960
You hugged me

598
00:31:58,180 --> 00:31:59,970
just to hide the gun

599
00:32:00,060 --> 00:32:01,520
and avoid the risk, right?

600
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,280
Am I right, Zhuo Ran?

601
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:08,640
No.

602
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:11,180
At that moment,

603
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:12,480
I wanted to give you some comfort.

604
00:32:16,670 --> 00:32:17,720
I'm going upstairs.

605
00:32:35,080 --> 00:32:36,350
Have you found Gui?

606
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:38,560
You're asking me?

607
00:32:41,390 --> 00:32:43,520
He ran away under your nose.
Why are you asking me?

608
00:32:43,780 --> 00:32:45,060
The situation was a chaos.

609
00:32:45,150 --> 00:32:46,520
It was chaotic, yes.

610
00:32:48,870 --> 00:32:50,780
You've been making errors
in the past few missions.

611
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:52,530
Don't tell me it's an accident.

612
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:55,960
What else could it be?

613
00:32:56,180 --> 00:32:57,490
What do you think it is?

614
00:32:58,300 --> 00:32:59,730
Don't think that you can
check and balance Old Master

615
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:01,120
by releasing Gui.

616
00:33:01,870 --> 00:33:03,500
If you don't want your mum...

617
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:04,740
Don't talk about my mum!

618
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:05,770
For your mum's sake,

619
00:33:05,860 --> 00:33:08,280
you'd better stop playing tricks!

620
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:30,570
Old Master.

621
00:33:30,860 --> 00:33:32,640
[Are you done with Gui?]

622
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:34,610
I'm sorry.

623
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:40,250
[You know that I hate apologies the most.]

624
00:33:41,390 --> 00:33:42,320
I know.

625
00:33:42,590 --> 00:33:43,090
However,

626
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,730
though Gui escaped,

627
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:47,240
we finally got to meet Xia Guang Yuan.

628
00:33:47,430 --> 00:33:49,850
He's changed his mind about me
due to the incident.

629
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,290
Hence,

630
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:53,020
it's not completely a bust.

631
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:56,020
What went wrong in the process?

632
00:33:57,210 --> 00:33:58,140
Liang Mu Ze.

633
00:33:58,340 --> 00:33:59,290
Who?

634
00:33:59,370 --> 00:34:00,690
[He's the Chinese military officer]

635
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:03,180
who I had bugs installed at his place.

636
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,760
Xia Chu is living at his place.

637
00:34:04,860 --> 00:34:06,080
They're quite close.

638
00:34:06,340 --> 00:34:07,850
Because of him,

639
00:34:07,990 --> 00:34:09,330
Gui escaped.

640
00:34:09,420 --> 00:34:11,340
[His presence has made my attempt]

641
00:34:11,430 --> 00:34:13,240
[to approach Xia Chu even harder.]

642
00:34:13,580 --> 00:34:15,080
I wanted to kill him before

643
00:34:15,220 --> 00:34:16,439
but I failed.

644
00:34:16,910 --> 00:34:17,919
He's a Special Forces soldier

645
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:19,330
and he usually live in the military camp.

646
00:34:19,470 --> 00:34:20,810
It's difficult to go near him.

647
00:34:20,899 --> 00:34:22,089
Even if I get to approach him,

648
00:34:22,189 --> 00:34:23,320
it would be

649
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:24,890
too risky

650
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:25,859
to take action in China.

651
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:27,260
Unless...

652
00:34:27,350 --> 00:34:28,399
[Unless what?]

653
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:29,580
Unless we can find a chance

654
00:34:29,669 --> 00:34:31,480
to end him

655
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:32,919
when he receives training abroad.

656
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:34,750
The difficulty

657
00:34:34,859 --> 00:34:36,050
[will be much lower.]

658
00:34:36,460 --> 00:34:38,120
End him abroad?

659
00:34:40,910 --> 00:34:41,790
Zhuo Ran.

660
00:34:42,109 --> 00:34:43,600
[You're really something.]

661
00:34:43,870 --> 00:34:45,250
Just by one line,

662
00:34:45,339 --> 00:34:47,089
you passed the problem to me.

663
00:34:48,330 --> 00:34:50,600
You can send Long Yi.

664
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,700
Are you trying to get rid of me?

665
00:34:52,790 --> 00:34:54,240
You serve no purpose here.

666
00:34:54,870 --> 00:34:55,970
[Enough.]

667
00:34:58,140 --> 00:34:59,260
[Your mission]

668
00:34:59,339 --> 00:35:01,689
[is to look for Gui
and nail Xia Guang Yuan.]

669
00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:04,280
As for Liang Mu Ze who may spoil our plan,

670
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:10,800
send his particulars to me.

671
00:35:11,170 --> 00:35:12,190
Got it.

672
00:35:16,580 --> 00:35:17,840
What should we do?

673
00:35:19,260 --> 00:35:20,840
It's not difficult to trace Gui.

674
00:35:21,580 --> 00:35:23,080
It's easy for you to say.

675
00:35:24,940 --> 00:35:26,930
Keep a close eye on
the police and Xia Guang Yuan.

676
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:29,180
The police are looking for him
and he's looking for Xia Guang Yuan.

677
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,720
We'll find something eventually.

678
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:57,050
What on earth is this?

679
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:05,920
Who is she?

680
00:36:08,510 --> 00:36:09,640
Meet each other.

681
00:36:10,220 --> 00:36:12,600
She's Liang Mu Ze's cousin.
Her name is Liang Shao Xue.

682
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,360
Be careful.

683
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:16,040
Don't let her crush you to death.

684
00:36:16,990 --> 00:36:18,530
This is my place!

685
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:20,670
Look after her. I need to take a rest.

686
00:36:21,980 --> 00:36:22,860
Please don't leave.

687
00:36:56,740 --> 00:36:59,450
Where is this?

688
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:07,960
What's wrong?

689
00:37:08,470 --> 00:37:09,840
It has nothing to do with me.

690
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:13,850
Where is this?

691
00:37:14,730 --> 00:37:15,910
This...

692
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,660
This is Liang Mu Ze's place.

693
00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:19,440
How is it possible?

694
00:37:19,750 --> 00:37:21,570
No way Mu Ze has a pet cat.

695
00:37:21,670 --> 00:37:24,330
It licked my face!

696
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:27,090
Don't be dramatic.

697
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,520
Calm down.

698
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:30,840
It's early in the morning.

699
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:32,170
Don't make a ruckus.

700
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:33,540
Don't irritate our neighbour

701
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:34,860
or they may report it to the police.

702
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:36,460
Leave me alone!

703
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:38,170
I'm about to explode!

704
00:37:45,260 --> 00:37:47,030
Calm down.

705
00:37:48,950 --> 00:37:50,650
You're completely awake.

706
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:51,820
If I hadn't woken up,

707
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,810
I might have been sold off
without knowing it.

708
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:57,040
Do you remember
yesterday, in the afternoon,

709
00:37:57,130 --> 00:37:59,070
you suddenly fell asleep
at the corridor in the hospital?

710
00:38:00,340 --> 00:38:02,520
Falling asleep is normal.

711
00:38:03,270 --> 00:38:04,540
I was dealing with jet lag.

712
00:38:04,660 --> 00:38:05,940
I didn't say that it's abnormal.

713
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,690
I just want to remind you that

714
00:38:07,940 --> 00:38:09,490
when you were in a deep sleep,

715
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,770
it was me

716
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,740
who brought you home

717
00:38:12,830 --> 00:38:14,450
despite being completely
burnt out after a night shift.

718
00:38:14,540 --> 00:38:15,580
Not only did you not thank me,

719
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:16,300
you're dubious of me.

720
00:38:16,390 --> 00:38:17,720
You suspected that I would sell you off!

721
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:19,540
Fine, it's okay.

722
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:20,490
You can question me all you want.

723
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:21,600
But now,

724
00:38:21,750 --> 00:38:22,460
I beg of you.

725
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:23,780
Will you keep quiet

726
00:38:23,870 --> 00:38:25,540
and let me take a nap?

727
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:26,500
That's because I need to work

728
00:38:26,590 --> 00:38:27,900
in the afternoon.

729
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:28,860
Okay?

730
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,280
Repeat!

731
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:36,250
-What?
-Repeat

732
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:37,560
the last word.

733
00:38:39,420 --> 00:38:40,900
I said so many things.

734
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:41,860
The last...

735
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,810
What did I say?

736
00:38:44,820 --> 00:38:48,920
I said I need to work in the afternoon.

737
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,570
Okay?

738
00:38:52,270 --> 00:38:54,250
OK?

739
00:38:54,990 --> 00:38:57,540
What should I do? I forgot about OK!

740
00:38:57,630 --> 00:38:59,880
How could I forgot OK?

741
00:39:00,100 --> 00:39:03,010
My OK!

742
00:39:07,900 --> 00:39:08,880
Report.

743
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:10,720
Come in.

744
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,160
Brigade Commander.

745
00:39:15,730 --> 00:39:17,690
The police have forwarded the summary

746
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:19,210
of the action to me.

747
00:39:19,310 --> 00:39:21,120
I'm waiting for
a detailed report from you.

748
00:39:22,410 --> 00:39:24,200
Something happened in the process.

749
00:39:24,300 --> 00:39:25,960
However, it went on smoothly in general.

750
00:39:26,260 --> 00:39:27,200
Sure, it's okay.

751
00:39:27,300 --> 00:39:27,940
Later,

752
00:39:28,030 --> 00:39:29,570
please submit a report in detail.

753
00:39:30,170 --> 00:39:30,970
By the way,

754
00:39:31,050 --> 00:39:33,200
have an internal meeting

755
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,600
with everyone who took part in the action

756
00:39:34,830 --> 00:39:35,960
to conclude the matter.

757
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:36,820
Yes.

758
00:39:36,910 --> 00:39:37,700
Also,

759
00:39:37,790 --> 00:39:39,980
I received instruction
from the higher authorities

760
00:39:40,120 --> 00:39:42,480
to send a team to
the Central Asian military training

761
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:44,360
which will be held by Willick
at the end of the month.

762
00:39:44,560 --> 00:39:45,590
End of the month?

763
00:39:45,830 --> 00:39:46,930
We don't have much time.

764
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:49,080
You'll be leading the team
during the training camp.

765
00:39:49,550 --> 00:39:50,520
How long will it take?

766
00:39:50,930 --> 00:39:52,230
It's tentatively scheduled for a week.

767
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:55,030
However,
it depends on the training progress.

768
00:39:55,650 --> 00:39:56,490
Do you have any question?

769
00:39:56,570 --> 00:39:57,450
No.

770
00:40:00,710 --> 00:40:03,040
Get ready.
Military reform is just around the corner.

771
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:04,850
This is a rare opportunity.

772
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:06,530
Don't make any mistake.

773
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:08,290
Yes, sir.

774
00:40:16,890 --> 00:40:18,120
[Can you stay by her side]

775
00:40:18,220 --> 00:40:19,640
[twenty-four hours a day?]

776
00:40:20,130 --> 00:40:22,110
[When I am by her side,]

777
00:40:22,390 --> 00:40:24,010
[what can you do for her]

778
00:40:24,150 --> 00:40:25,890
[being in the military camp?]

779
00:40:46,490 --> 00:40:47,990
Brigade Commander
wants me to check on you.

780
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:50,330
Why?

781
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:53,220
He thinks that you're not in a good mood

782
00:40:53,310 --> 00:40:54,480
after executing the mission.

783
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:04,170
It turns out that
Xia Chu is also suffering from insomnia.

784
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,060
Why can't she fall asleep?

785
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:07,530
It's because of her first love.

786
00:41:08,290 --> 00:41:10,600
You...

787
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:13,330
Are you in a bad mood?

788
00:41:14,180 --> 00:41:15,080
No.

789
00:41:18,720 --> 00:41:19,860
I'm worried.

790
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:22,290
I think this guy

791
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:23,990
has some hidden agendas.

792
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,080
Hello.

793
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:41,270
[Old Master.]

794
00:41:41,510 --> 00:41:42,260
[The military]

795
00:41:42,350 --> 00:41:44,690
[invited the special forces of China
for a training camp.]

796
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:46,800
[It seems that]

797
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,540
[the person who you're interested in]

798
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:49,880
[is in the participant list.]

799
00:41:50,420 --> 00:41:52,780
[I've sent you his particulars
through email.]

800
00:41:53,090 --> 00:41:54,310
You may take a look.

801
00:41:55,660 --> 00:41:56,680
Got it.

802
00:42:26,450 --> 00:42:27,870
Judging from the X-ray,

803
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:30,140
it's aortic regurgitation.

804
00:42:30,860 --> 00:42:31,930
You can't wait

805
00:42:32,020 --> 00:42:33,030
any longer.

806
00:42:33,430 --> 00:42:35,210
Many problems will manifest as time pass.

807
00:42:35,390 --> 00:42:36,520
Therefore, I suggest that

808
00:42:36,750 --> 00:42:38,610
you undergo the surgery
as soon as possible.

809
00:42:39,350 --> 00:42:40,410
I can't do that, doctor.

810
00:42:40,500 --> 00:42:42,410
I'm really occupied at work.

811
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:43,770
I can't make it.

812
00:42:43,940 --> 00:42:45,730
Let me be frank.

813
00:42:46,070 --> 00:42:48,090
You will have to undergo the surgery
sooner or later.

814
00:42:48,310 --> 00:42:50,530
It's better to do it early.

815
00:42:52,160 --> 00:42:54,270
I think my body is doing fine.

816
00:42:54,380 --> 00:42:55,600
It's okay.

817
00:42:56,100 --> 00:42:58,080
Why are you here if everything is okay?

818
00:42:58,660 --> 00:43:00,210
Why do you come to me if you're okay?

819
00:43:00,300 --> 00:43:02,370
I'm busy.
Don't take up my time for nothing.

820
00:43:02,680 --> 00:43:04,270
Doctor, don't be mad.

821
00:43:04,360 --> 00:43:05,510
I'm not mad.

822
00:43:05,670 --> 00:43:06,800
It's your body.

823
00:43:07,310 --> 00:43:08,770
You should think for yourself.

824
00:43:09,330 --> 00:43:11,450
I know. How about this?

825
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:12,650
Please prescribe some medicine for me.

826
00:43:12,740 --> 00:43:13,740
I'll start with taking medicine.

827
00:43:13,830 --> 00:43:14,700
What do you think?

828
00:43:14,790 --> 00:43:15,460
Please do me a favour.

829
00:43:15,550 --> 00:43:16,920
Thank you. Please do me a favour.

830
00:43:18,910 --> 00:43:20,100
Don't stretch yourself thin.

831
00:43:22,630 --> 00:43:25,050
If you are down with flu or diarrhoea,

832
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:26,520
you must seek medical help
soonest the possible.

833
00:43:26,740 --> 00:43:27,170
Sure.

834
00:43:27,260 --> 00:43:29,220
If your heart contracted a virus,

835
00:43:29,310 --> 00:43:30,540
it would become a serious problem.

836
00:43:30,630 --> 00:43:31,920
-Okay.
-Bear it in mind.

837
00:43:32,700 --> 00:43:33,580
Okay.

838
00:43:34,160 --> 00:43:35,040
Okay.

839
00:43:35,610 --> 00:43:37,980
Thank you, doctor.

840
00:43:49,940 --> 00:43:51,720
That's all for today. Come again tomorrow.

841
00:43:52,050 --> 00:43:54,380
Dr Zhang, it's me.

842
00:43:59,030 --> 00:44:00,180
It's you.

843
00:44:00,270 --> 00:44:01,450
Yes.

844
00:44:02,110 --> 00:44:03,050
Where is Xiao Jun?

845
00:44:03,870 --> 00:44:05,850
Xiao Jun has gone to school.

846
00:44:06,390 --> 00:44:07,850
I'm out for groceries shopping.

847
00:44:07,950 --> 00:44:09,330
That's why I brought you

848
00:44:09,420 --> 00:44:10,940
some steamed cakes which I just made.

849
00:44:11,030 --> 00:44:11,780
Try it.

850
00:44:11,860 --> 00:44:12,740
Great.

851
00:44:13,280 --> 00:44:15,170
I was thinking
what I should have for lunch.

852
00:44:16,190 --> 00:44:17,210
Thank you.

853
00:44:17,540 --> 00:44:18,450
You're welcome.

854
00:44:18,540 --> 00:44:19,940
I should be the one to thank you.

855
00:44:20,020 --> 00:44:21,960
Xiao Jun recovered well after the surgery.

856
00:44:22,060 --> 00:44:22,940
Therefore,

857
00:44:23,030 --> 00:44:25,840
I'm here to thank you officially.

858
00:44:26,010 --> 00:44:27,680
Don't do that.

859
00:44:27,850 --> 00:44:30,020
What are you doing?
You don't have to do that.

860
00:44:34,860 --> 00:44:35,920
Well...

861
00:44:36,100 --> 00:44:37,800
I'll not take up your time.

862
00:44:37,900 --> 00:44:39,120
Enjoy the food.

863
00:44:39,330 --> 00:44:40,750
Sure, thank you.

864
00:44:41,380 --> 00:44:42,600
I'm leaving.

865
00:44:44,190 --> 00:44:45,580
-Goodbye.
-Sure.

866
00:44:45,660 --> 00:44:47,370
Chen Meng Zhen.

867
00:44:50,930 --> 00:44:52,200
My name is Zhang Yi Chi.

868
00:44:52,540 --> 00:44:53,660
The next time we meet each other,

869
00:44:53,750 --> 00:44:54,810
you may address me by my first name.

870
00:44:54,920 --> 00:44:57,060
You're being so polite all the time.

871
00:44:57,150 --> 00:44:58,250
You sound distant.

872
00:44:58,340 --> 00:45:00,040
We're almost the same age.

873
00:45:00,570 --> 00:45:01,720
The way you address me

874
00:45:01,810 --> 00:45:03,070
makes me sound old.

875
00:45:04,050 --> 00:45:05,660
Okay, I got it now.

876
00:45:06,840 --> 00:45:08,460
-I'll go now.
-Goodbye.

877
00:45:08,790 --> 00:45:10,050
Goodbye.
